Layer 3: Knowledge Graph & Semantic Layer
Status: Phase 2 (after Layer 2) Technology Stack: Neo4j 5.x Enterprise, Pinecone/Weaviate, FastAPI

Data Model:

Nodes: :Capability, :UseCase, :Persona, :ValueDriver
Relationships: :ENABLES, :BENEFITS, :DRIVES, :CONTRIBUTES_TO
Properties: embedding (1536-dim), confidence, source_url, extracted_at
GraphRAG Implementation:

Indexing Phase:
Entity embeddings stored
Leiden community detection (GDS)
LLM-generated community summaries
Hierarchical index built
Retrieval Phase:
Vector search (cosine similarity) → entry nodes
Graph traversal (BFS/DFS, 3-hop max) → connected subgraphs
Reranking by relevance
Citation support with source nodes
Global Queries: Use community summaries for broad questions (no vector search)
Semantic Layer:

Centralized metric definitions (YAML/JSON): ARR, NRR, CAC, LTV, Churn Rate
Row-level security: Filter by JWT claims
Column-level masking: Hide formula parameters for non-admins
API Endpoints:

POST /query/natural-language → {answer, citations, confidence}
POST /query/traverse → {subgraph, paths}
POST /query/value-tree → {capability, use_cases, personas, value_drivers, total_roi_potential}
GET /semantic/metrics
POST /semantic/calculate → Execute stored formulas
Performance Targets:

Single-hop: <50ms p95
Multi-hop (3 levels): <200ms p95
Vector + graph: <500ms p95
Concurrent: 1000+ connections
Graph size: 10M nodes, 100M relationships
Deliverables:

Neo4j schema and constraints
RDF → Neo4j ingestion pipeline
GraphRAG retrieval engine with caching
Semantic layer configuration
FastAPI application
Cypher query library (parameterized)
Monitoring: Query performance, cache hit rates
Acceptance Criteria:

Multi-hop reasoning accuracy >90% (vs 60% vector-only baseline)
Query latency targets under load
Zero Cypher injection (pen tested)
Semantic consistency: Same metric = same value
Full provenance trace <500ms
Layer 4: Agentic Workflow Engine
Status: Phase 3 (after Layer 3) Technology Stack: LangGraph, GPT-4o/Claude 3.5, Redis, Celery, python-docx/pptx, WeasyPrint

Workflow 1: Whitespace Analysis Agent

Input: {prospect_domain, prospect_ticker}
Steps: IngestProspect → ExtractInsights → MapToCapabilities → IdentifyWhitespace → GeneratePlan
Output: JSON account plan with whitespace opportunities, stakeholder map, entry strategy
Workflow 2: Dynamic ROI Calculator

Input: {opportunity_id, prospect_metrics}
Retrieves Value Tree from graph
Safely evaluates formula strings (numexpr)
Monte Carlo sensitivity analysis (best/worst/expected case)
Output: Deterministic ROI projection + risk assessment
Workflow 3: Business Case Generator

Input: ROI calculations, prospect context
Auto-generates: Executive Summary, Current State, Proposed Solution, Financial Analysis, Risk Mitigation, Next Steps
Formats: Markdown, DOCX, PDF, PPTX (10-15 slides)
Output: Consultant-grade document
Workflow 4: Provenance Audit Agent

Input: {output_id, output_type}
Traverses PROV-O graph backward
Shows: LLM calls → extractions → source documents
Displays confidence scores at each step
API: GET /audit/trace/{output_id}
Agent Orchestration:

LangGraph state machines with persistence
Tool registry: KG query, web search, calculator, document generator
Human-in-the-loop at critical points (approval gates)
API Endpoints:

POST /agents/whitespace → {workflow_id, status}
POST /agents/roi → {calculation_id, result}
POST /agents/business-case?format=pdf|docx|pptx → {document_url, pages}
GET /agents/status/{workflow_id}
POST /agents/{workflow_id}/approve → Resume or cancel
